  <title>Minimum CRS Score for Canada PR 2026 – What Score Do You Need for Express Entry?</title>
  <meta name="description" content="What is the minimum CRS score for Canada PR in 2026? No fixed minimum exists — but general draws average 491, French draws cut at 393, trades at 388. Full 2026 score guide, pathway comparison, and interactive eligibility checker." />
