                <div class="pw-score">388–430</div>
                <p class="pw-desc">Truck drivers (73300), Bus drivers (73310), Aircraft mechanics (72406), Air traffic controllers (72600). 2026 range: 388–430. Less frequent than healthcare or STEM draws.</p>
                <a class="pw-link" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/express-entry-draws">Latest Transport Draws →</a>
